{
  "stem": "17372.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 309.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they were making quite often segregation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People who didn't have the Kennkarte-- this is the card with the stamp that they work somewhere-- they deport them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't know then what we know now.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We thought they go to other camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we've never seen them again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some very young children and not strong-looking physically, unable to work-- they've been segregating them and take away.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Didn't have a clue then, didn't have a clue.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About '42, end of '42.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The, the Jewish police came and took them to certain Platz, place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they took them out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We never see-- I didn't-- we didn't, didn't have contact with them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "See, they had-- there was a big place, and Platz [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Gold, ?] they called in Cracow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was also the polish chemist on the corner, there, who watch all these [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] segregations.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He help a lot Jews, this-- Pankevitch was his name in Cracow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We play quite often there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the commandant of Jewish police, that Spira, was coming there, some or other important people, drinking vodka from the files, you know, chemists-- they got in chemist, from those files drink.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] then we had to-- not allowed to go after 10 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we had to go under guard back home and held a-- everything very close.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What was told--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They have been told that they are going to other camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They told them to take bags.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But, but as soon as they leave, they took away the bags.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You've seen on television-- on film how they have been doing this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They took the whole possessions and over to oven.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We can't resist with guns standing, police with dogs barking.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't have a clue.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
